            "title": "盤中速報 - Take-Two互動軟體(TTWO-US)大跌5.05%，報227.19美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Take-Two互動軟體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTWO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTWO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTWO-US</a>)截至台北時間30日23:09股價下跌12.08美元，報227.19美元，跌幅5.05%，成交量584,596（股），盤中最高價238.15美元、最低價227.19美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.23%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.3%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.3%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Take-Two互動軟體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTWO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTWO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTWO-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+0.86%</li> <li>近 1 月：-4.9%</li> <li>近 3 月：-3.4%</li> <li>近 6 月：+8.57%</li> <li>今年以來：-5.02%</li></ul></section></main>",
